data.description: Charming Big Bear cabin, warmly decorated and fully furnished.  This home is a 2 bed 1 bath home offers the perfect weekend getaway. Plenty of room to sleep.   Great views of Gold Mountain off the back deck.  This home has many upgrades, new flooring downstairs,  exterior and interior paint, updated kitchen with new appliances, and new light fixtures.  Don't miss out on this one!
